
 iOS Apps Automation Testing with Appium

1) Download Appium Server

2) Install XCode to compile the app on suitable iPhone/iPad

3) Launch iPhone Simulator

4) Setup Appium maven Project with Appium Jars

5) Desired Capabilities needs to invoke app on the iPhone

6) Understand how to inspect object of iOS App using Appium Inspector

7) Build Appium Automation Script for Functional Testing of iOS App

8) How to automate dropDown, Text Edit boxes, Steppers, Buttons, Menu's Alerts, 
   How to scroll
   How to swipe
   How to Long Press
   How to Tap
   How to perform 3dtouch event and automate slides